“Betaab Dil” is a heart-touching romantic Hindi song that brings back the golden era of 90s Bollywood music. Sung and composed by Sarit Dutta, this soulful melody beautifully captures the emotions of love, longing, and separation. The heartfelt lyrics by Dr. Uma Naveen Mehta paint a timeless picture of a betaab (restless) heart waiting for its beloved.

If you miss the charm of classic love songs, “Betaab Dil” will take you straight back to that nostalgic era of melody and emotion.

🎧 Experience “Betaab Dil” — A Pure Hindi Romantic Love Song
Close your eyes, feel the rhythm, and let this song remind you of the beautiful simplicity of true love. Perfect for anyone who believes in eternal romance and misses the soulful tunes of the 90s

snippet.title: ARMY OF THE CHRIST | Official Trailer | SWJC FILMS
snippet.description:
Written and Directed by Joshua Samuel, Army of the Christ is a groundbreaking Gospel feature film presented by SWJC FILMS — marking Pakistan’s first-ever Gospel cinematic experience.

The film stars Mathew Javed, Joshua Samuel, Khurram Patras, Mehran Zaib, Elishba Samuel, Sohail Waris, Shahbaz Gulzar, Yashwa Akram, and Rachel Mehran. 

Army of the Christ is inspired by an imaginary depiction of Matthew 24 from the Bible — a cinematic vision brought to life to inspire and awaken believers to rise and stand strong as The Army of the Christ.

Produced by Pastor Samuel Payara and captured through the lens of Director of Photography Sohail Joseph, the film blends faith, emotion, and cinematic excellence to create a historic milestone in Pakistan’s film industry — a bold step towards Gospel storytelling on the big screen.
